column14:
Maci is an excellent role model in school and the community.  She works hard and is very diligent about her academics.  Maci is active at LSW in cheer, she is part of a peer leadership group and has assisted in some volunteer opportunities while in my class.  
Maci makes wise social decisions and would represent Lincoln G.O.L.D. in a positive manner!!
